'''Susmita''' is an [[India]]n name usually used for females. Susmita originates from the ancient [[Indian culture]]. [[Benagali]] people commonly use this name for their daughter or sisters. Meaning of Susmita in Bengali language is "Women having lovely [[smile]]".

There are so many famous ladies in [[Indian History]] having their name as Susmita.

